==Internet Tough Guy==

The "Seattle Anti-Flake Community Action Initiative" has long had Cadmus on their watch list, citing his [[drama whore| absurdly loud]] participation in some of Seattle's [[gay|gayest]] fringe culture events. After being banned from most [[pagan]] gatherings for being an [[internet tough guy]], he turned all his attention to the [[internet]]- the better to get his mind off the wife he married (for cover) and the screaming child that was accidentally produced before the marriage died [[lesbian bed death]].
==Brother Jordan, Buddha, and Bill==

cadmus began his [[Asperger's_syndrome| Ass pie]] career on the [[internet]] after "Brother Jordan" baptized him into the [[mythunderstood| gnostic]] religion. He began as a Gnostic missionary, spreading the word of [[rape]] and the true [[Tom Cruise|Christ]]. His career as a Gnostic only lasted 43 minutes, however, because he had discovered [[buddha|buddhism]] less than an hour later, and converted.

Before his powerful conversion to [[mythunderstood|Gnosticism]] and then to [[buddha|Buddhism]], Cadmus was [[pagan|Wiccan]]. Before he was Wiccan, he was dipped in [[semen|this stuff]] and slowly slid up the asshole of [[Bill Gates| this man]], working as a project supervisor. According to his profoundly mentally handicapped LJ, he still works for [[satan| Bill.]]

